## Custom Event Data

### Passing Data with Events

You can pass custom data via event detail:

```csharp
// Application/Services/TodoService.cs
_eventBus.Fire(DomainEvents.TodoCreated, new { id = todo.Id, title = todo.Title });
```

**JavaScript listener:**

```html
<script>
document.body.addEventListener('entity.created:todo', (e) => {
    console.log('Todo ID:', e.detail.id);
    console.log('Todo Title:', e.detail.title);
});
</script>
```

