## Migration from Monolith

**Monolith (event names in Web layer):**
```csharp
// Web/Events/EventNames.cs
public static string TodoCreated => "entity.created:todo";

// Web/Controllers/TodosController.cs
_events.Fire(EventNames.TodoCreated);
```

**Layered (event names in Domain layer):**
```csharp
// Domain/Events/DomainEvents.cs
public static string TodoCreated => "entity.created:todo";

// Application/Services/TodoService.cs
_eventBus.Fire(DomainEvents.TodoCreated);

// Web/Events/SwapEventChains.cs
events.Chain(DomainEvents.TodoCreated, "ui.refreshList", "ui.showToast");
```

